# Apify JavaScript Integration

Apify provides a complete JavaScript ecosystem for web scraping and automation. Here's how it works:

## Core Components

### 1. **Apify SDK** (Main Library)
```javascript
import { Actor } from 'apify';

await Actor.init();

// Your scraping logic here
const data = await scraper.run();

await Actor.pushData(data);
await Actor.exit();
```

### 2. **Key Features**

#### Request Queue Management
```javascript
import { Actor } from 'apify';

const requestQueue = await Actor.openRequestQueue();

// Add URLs to process
await requestQueue.addRequest({
  url: 'https://example.com',
  uniqueKey: 'page-1',
});

// Process requests
while (true) {
  const request = await requestQueue.fetchNextRequest();
  if (!request) break;

  // Handle request
  await request.marksucceeded();
}
```

#### Data Storage
```javascript
// Push data to default dataset
await Actor.pushData({
  title: 'Product Name',
  price: 99.99,
  url: 'https://example.com/product'
});

// Get dataset
const dataset = await Actor.openDataset('my-dataset');
await dataset.pushData(items);
```

#### Key-Value Store
```javascript
const kvStore = await Actor.openKeyValueStore();

// Save state
await kvStore.setValue('crawler-state', {
  lastUrl: 'https://example.com/page-10',
  processedCount: 150
});

// Retrieve state
const state = await kvStore.getValue('crawler-state');
```

### 3. **Browser Automation Integration**

```javascript
import { Actor } from 'apify';
import { PuppeteerCrawler } from 'apify';

await Actor.init();

const crawler = new PuppeteerCrawler({
  maxRequestsPerCrawl: 100,

  async requestHandler({ request, page }) {
    const title = await page.title();
    const data = await page.evaluate(() => {
      return {
        heading: document.querySelector('h1').textContent,
        paragraphs: Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('p'))
          .map(p => p.textContent)
      };
    });

    await Actor.pushData({
      url: request.url,
      title,
      ...data
    });
  },

  async errorHandler({ request, error }) {
    console.error(`Request failed: ${request.url}`, error);
  }
});

await crawler.run(['https://example.com']);
await Actor.exit();
```

### 4. **Cheerio Crawler** (Lightweight)
```javascript
import { CheerioCrawler } from 'apify';

const crawler = new CheerioCrawler({
  async requestHandler({ request, $, body }) {
    const products = [];

    $('div.product').each((i, el) => {
      products.push({
        name: $(el).find('.name').text(),
        price: $(el).find('.price').text(),
      });
    });

    await Actor.pushData(products);
  }
});

await crawler.run(['https://example.com']);
```

